  "task": "# Relay stage 1: Ideate\nTask: fix-stage-timer\nWorking directory: /tmp/nix-shell.YWSHjG/visual-relay/wt/f68ff1f862b4/plan-20260628082230/fix-stage-timer\n\n## Task input\n# Fix Stage Timer\n\nIf I click between different tasks, the timer for a given stage gets reset to 0 (e.g., the verify stage in the screenshot kept going back to 0 when clicking away and then back to the task). Fix.\n\n## Manifest\n(not set yet)\n\n## Task context\n### Screenshot 2026-06-26 at 1.25.04\u202fPM.png (530217 bytes, not inlined)\n\n## Prior stages\n\n\nEnd your reply with a single fenced ```json block, nothing after it, matching: { \"summary\": string, \"options\": string[] }",
